Each provide a different size


Paragraph Element
<p> The 'p' refers to the paragraph </p>

Comment and uncommenting HTML
<!-- These symbols are needed to be at the end and start of the comment you want hidden.   -->

Comments can be a way to hide information in the code without impacting it.


